title: Dakine Girls Wheeled Duffle
description:
Check out 360° views of the 2012 Girls Wheeled Duffle travel bag in our Skylar print.
Travel Bag Features:
- U-shaped opening for easy access
- Zippered end pockets
- Retractable handle
- Replaceable urethane wheels
- Locking zipper cars
- Clear window ID holder on back panel
